    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《突袭大乱斗》是一款融合了roguelite元素的2D动作休闲游戏，玩家可以选择一个角色，与一波又一波的敌人战斗。通过神秘的自动售货机购买新的武器和装备，升级你的武器库。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >            <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271250/extras/0ecd63547259c0c2b6fbdad3bb221884.apng?t=1770813138\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271250/extras/0ecd63547259c0c2b6fbdad3bb221884.poster.avif?t=1770813138\" class=\"bb_img\" width=160 height=160 /></picture></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271250/extras/0a62a96c13d72ba14c292534f9379602.poster.avif?t=1770813138\" width=160 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271250/extras/0a62a96c13d72ba14c292534f9379602.webm?t=1770813138\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271250/extras/5cdfa82279dbb6adf485926e11dddc65.apng?t=1770813138\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271250/extras/5cdfa82279dbb6adf485926e11dddc65.poster.avif?t=1770813138\" class=\"bb_img\" width=160 height=160 /></picture></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271250/extras/eeef7cafd411aefbc28368509f209fc3.poster.avif?t=1770813138\" width=160 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271250/extras/eeef7cafd411aefbc28368509f209fc3.webm?t=1770813138\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在激烈的战斗中，你将面对僵尸、机器人、外星人和其他威胁，解锁升级和独特角色。每个角色都拥有专属的被动技能和独特的属性，以契合你的游戏风格。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >超过 60 种物品可供你打造专属装备；</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 除了猫咪托比之外，还有 9 个可解锁角色； </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4 张拥有独特机制的地图； </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >16 种不同的敌人和 4 个会不断变强的 Boss； </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >14 种可解锁的升级。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271250/extras/4e9ff7bfe71830a1aacc73b709e02988.avif?t=1770813138\" width=1280 height=160 /></span></p></li></ul>",
